$interpreted: Dumb Bear Soldier: Heelllooo~~

Jasmine: My cousin Rose is not at home right now.
If you are here for her, door's over there. See yourself out.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Rose? Who is Rose?

Jasmine: Everyone always here for Rose's beauty.
Are you not one of those guys?
Dumb Bear Soldier: I'm here to see a Jasmine~~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Is Jasmine home~?
Jasmine: What do you want to see me for?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Are you Jasmine?
Dumb Bear Soldier: That's awesome~~
Jasmine: What is that weird sound?
Dumb Bear Soldier: I'm very hungry... I heard you cook delicious food. Can you let me have a bite? No, two bites...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Umm~ Two bites not quite enough too. I'm really starving~
Jasmine: How did you know I like cooking?
Dumb Bear Soldier: It's that... that... who's the guy that told me?
Dumb Bear Soldier: AH~~~!
Dumb Bear Soldier: I forgot his name~
Jasmine: Hmph, I get it. You lying on purpose to approach me. Your idea is to get to Rose through me, right?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Eh? Rose good at cooking too?
Jasmine: Hmph! I'm not going to tell you anything about Rose!

Dumb Bear Soldier: Ummm... I think... I made her mad?
Two bites too greedy after all. Should've just asked for one bite...
Dumb Bear Soldier: What do I do what do I do, Jasmine is mad...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Jasmine forgot her lunch box!
Dumb Bear Soldier: ......
Dumb Bear Soldier: No good, this is Jasmine's lunch box. Must, NOT, eat it!
Dumb Bear Soldier: If I eat it, Jasmine'll be hungry. I have to deliver this to her.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Jasmine~ You forgot your lunch box. Jasmine~~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Jasmine~ Jasmine~~
Jasmine: Stop following me!
Jasmine: Enough is enough! Just leave me alone!
Dumb Bear Soldier: But, lunch box...
Jasmine: I'm not going to tell you what kind of lunch box Rose likes!
Dumb Bear Soldier: No, I'm not... I'm talking about this...

Jasmine: Shut up! Don't talk to me.
And stop following me too!
Dumb Bear Soldier: Hmmmmmm!
Dumb Bear Soldier: Hm! Hm!
Jasmine: Why do you keep making that "Hm Hm" noise? Huh? The thing you're holding, isn't that my lunch box? ......
Jasmine: Why'd you hit me!?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Hmmmm! ......
Jasmine: Are you alright?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Oww it hurt...
Dumb Bear Soldier: Ah, no talking!
Jasmine: Could it be... I told you to shut up, so you actually shut up and stop talking?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Hmm~ Hmm~
Jasmine: ... Sorry. I shouldn't have told you to shut up.
Jasmine: Are you okay? Did you get hurt?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Not okay~
Jasmine: What's the matter? Did monsters injure you?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Lunch box... spilled everywhere...
Jasmine: So you followed me all the way here just so you can give this lunch box back to me?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Because no lunch box, Jasmine will be hungry.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Hungry is bad. Need to eat well to do things.
Jasmine: ......
Jasmine: Since being hungry is bad...
Jasmine: ... then let's eat this together~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Yeah~ lunch box time~ lunch box time~
Dumb Bear Soldier: Lunch box~ Lunch box~
